.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, milk, water
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |       2       |  3  |
| Beverage   | juice | milk | water |

