.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, board-games, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | board-games | skydiving | woodworking |

